title: Black Panther - The Most Dangerous Man Alive 524 (2011) (Digital
description:
Black Panther - The Most Dangerous Man Alive 524 (2011) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)


It started as the American Panther, now it's six-Armed Panther swinging into action. The arachnid infection griping Manhattan hits T'Challa but it doesn't mean he'll stop trying to protect Hell's Kitchen. When Overdrive breaks into the quarantine zone, your friendly neighborhood Spider-Panther swings into a deadly race across the streets of New York City. The Spidey villain stolen that's worth smashing through a hero-protected border but the bigger question is why the lethal Lady Bullseye keeps trying to keep him from getting back out
